{
  "newspaper_id": "lankadeepa-lk",
  "url": "https://www.lankadeepa.lk/latest_news/\u2018\u2018\u0d85\u0db4\u0dda-\u0d85\u0db1\u0dd4\u0dc1\u0dcf\u0dc3\u0db1\u0dcf-\u0db4\u0dd2\u0dc5\u0dd2\u0d9c\u0dad\u0dca\u0dad\u0dcf-\u0db1\u0db8\u0dca-\u0db8\u0dd9\u0dc4\u0dd9\u0db8-\u0dc0\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0dda-\u0db1\u0dd1\u2018\u2018/1-615608",
  "time_ut": 1656498851,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u2018\u2018\u0d85\u0db4\u0dda \u0d85\u0db1\u0dd4\u0dc1\u0dcf\u0dc3\u0db1\u0dcf \u0db4\u0dd2\u0dc5\u0dd2\u0d9c\u0dad\u0dca\u0dad\u0dcf \u0db1\u0db8\u0dca \u0db8\u0dd9\u0dc4\u0dd9\u0db8 \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0dda \u0db1\u0dd1\u2018\u2018",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "\"This would not have happened if we had accepted our advice.\"",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Mahanayake Thero of the Gnanaratana Asgiriya Chapter in Warakagoda said that the country was in such a catastrophic situation that the rulers did not heed the advice given by the Maha Sangha.",
        "The Supreme Buddha was also insulted. The monks are a group of people who can endure humiliation and work. There are many people living among us who have sinful ideas that offend noble services. Human beings say that only a few people can think intelligently and understand that this is good and this is bad and most can be considered as extremists.",
        "Even the little children here today know the tragedy that has befallen our country today. We also know the reason for that. We are sorry about that but there is nothing to do. As monks, we gave them the advice and admonition they needed at the right time. But we seemed to ignore them.",
        "If it goes this way, this country will be on the verge of destruction. We explained all that to them. But it is very clear that they do not care. Therefore, the monks of this country have realized that it is useless to go and talk about something that is not being done. All educated people are worried about the situation in this country."
      ],
      "title_ents": [],
